cdata.name: LeadCoin
cdata.desc:
LeadCoin empowers businesses to sell their unused leads and buy hot leads from other businesses. Sellers automatically share their unused leads in real-time. LeadCoins matching algorithm then analyzes and matches leads to buyers. Leads who didnt match one business, are now the perfect match for another.

The LDC Token represents the right to acquire leads from other businesses in the network.
